Glencore Sees ‘Strong Demand’ for Coal on China, India Demand

-- B y   M a r e k   S t r z e l e c k i
-- 
2011-08-25T13:36:13Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-25/glencore-sees-strong-demand-for-coal-on-china-india-demand.html
Glencore International Plc forecasts
“strong demand worldwide” for coal as use rises in China and
 India , company executives including Chief Executive Officer Ivan Glasenberg said today on a conference call.  Europe  is also a growth market for the fuel after  Germany 
ordered the closure of reactors in March, the executives said,
according to a transcript of the call.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Marek Strzelecki in Warsaw 
 mstrzelecki1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Steve Voss at   sev@bloomberg.net  